snippet.title: Coffence 2018 Trailer
snippet.description:
Grab your cup and face your friends in a fast-paced blend of fighting games and twin-stick shooters.

Coffence's biggest update yet is coming to steam: Story Mode, new characters, new levels, new cups, steam achievements and a large cupful of fixes and upgrades.
